      <title>分析师称亚洲外汇和中国股市将受到特朗普关税的冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/asian-fx-chinese-stocks-to-be-hit-by-trump-tariffs-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布将对墨西哥、加拿大征收贸易税并提高对中国的关税后，交易员可能会重新评估其仓位，市场可能继续承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/asian-fx-chinese-stocks-to-be-hit-by-trump-tariffs-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 04:24:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
